column5: Local high-tech electronics manufacturing company looking for an experienced electronics circuit board assembly/soldering person.  Must be able to populate and solder high component count, complex printed circuit boards as well as assemble wiring harnesses and specialty cables.  Quality workmanship is paramount.  Must have a dedicated work ethic and work well in a team environment.  Please submit resume with references.  to [emailÂ protected]
